				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "Learned some error handling for JSParser. There were two files that did not parse. Both reported unexpected tokens.\n`state.js` at character 1853.\n`active.js` at character 1924.\nWhat they had in common is both are the first characters following an `if (condition) return`."
			},
